{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012Ck52ua8ntT37CFsChAVFr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016JKURLhAGsDDvGFvYnmcX2","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chrisraethke/projects/x-agent/.ralph/work-summary.txt","content":"# Work Summary — Spec 05: gha-agent\n\n## What was implemented\n\nCreated the gha-agent — a lean GitHub Actions workflow linter that runs `actionlint` on `.github/workflows/*.yml` and `*.yaml` files.\n\n### Files created:\n- `skills/gha-agent/scripts/gha-agent.sh` — main agent script (~140 lines total, ~100 lines domain code)\n- `skills/gha-agent/SKILL.md` — trigger language, allowed-tools, and usage docs\n- `tests/gha-agent/clean/scenario.env` + `.github/workflows/ci.yml` — passing fixture (valid workflow)\n- `tests/gha-agent/issues/scenario.env` + `.github/workflows/bad.yml` — failing fixture (unquoted expression `${{ github.event.inputs.name }}`)\n\n### Files modified:\n- `install.sh` — added `gha-agent` to SKILLS, actionlint dep check, and snippet line\n- `README.md` — added gha-agent row in Available Agents table, usage section, direct-use example, and skill reference\n\n## Deviations from work plan\n\nNone. Implementation follows the plan exactly.\n\n## Edge cases handled\n- No `.github/workflows/` directory: returns `SKIP` with explicit reason\n- `CHANGED_FILES` set but no workflow files match: returns `SKIP`\n- `CHANGED_FILES` filtering: only existing `.yml`/`.yaml` files under `.github/workflows/` are included\n- `--help`/`help`/`-h`: handled before `need actionlint` so it works without actionlint installed\n- Unknown commands: prints usage and exits 2\n- `RUN_LINT=0` in `all` mode: skips the lint step\n- `FAIL_FAST`: uses `should_continue()` from shared lib\n- Empty workflow files list via discovery: returns `SKIP`\n\n## Tests written/run\n- `tests/gha-agent/clean/` — would pass with exit 0 (valid workflow, actionlint passes)\n- `tests/gha-agent/issues/` — would fail with exit 1 (unquoted expression in workflow)\n- Both scenarios correctly SKIP when `actionlint` is not installed (REQUIRED_TOOLS gating)\n- `shellcheck --severity=warning` passes on gha-agent.sh\n- Full suite: all 18 scenarios pass (including all existing agents), 0 failures\n\n## Known limitations\n- `CHANGED_FILES` splits on whitespace; paths with spaces are not supported (matches convention used by all other agents)\n- Scenario tests require `actionlint` to be installed to run the actual lint checks; they SKIP gracefully when missing\n\n## Feedback Closure Matrix\nNo prior review issues exist for this spec (first implementation).\n\n## Exploration notes\nUpdated `.ralph/exploration.md`: added gha-agent entry to Key Files & Roles, updated install.sh description to include gha-agent.\n\n## Lessons Applied This Phase\n- help-before-need: Parsed help flags before `need actionlint` so `--help` works without actionlint installed (pattern from bash-agent and go-agent)\n- Followed existing agent patterns (bash-agent) for file discovery, structured output, and scenario fixture format\n\n## Suggestions for the REVIEW agent\n- Verify `--help` works without actionlint installed\n- The issue fixture uses unquoted `${{ github.event.inputs.name }}` which actionlint should flag\n- Verify SKIP behavior when no `.github/workflows/` directory exists\n- `CHANGED_FILES` scoping correctly filters to only `.yml`/`.yaml` under `.github/workflows/`\n- Single-step agent so `all` command routes through `run_lint` with `should_continue` guard\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":337,"cache_read_input_tokens":65273,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":337},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"04f1945e-7bf3-4940-ab64-46803dcd06b1","uuid":"de27fd